column2: SELECT so.specObjID, so.ra, so.dec, so.plate, so.mjd, so.fiberID, elp.Flux_Hb_#, elp.AoN_Hb_#, elp.Flux_NII_#, elp.FLUX_OIII_#, elp.AoN_NII_#, elp.Flux_Ha_#, elp.AoN_Ha_#, elp.AoN_OIII_#, elp.Flux_HeII_#, elp.AoN_HeII_#, so.z, so.snMedian_g, elp.V_Hb_#, elp.V_NII_#, elp.V_Ha_#, elp.V_OIII_#, elp.Flux_OI_#, elp.AoN_OI_#, elp.Flux_SII_#, elp.AoN_SII_#, elp.Flux_SII_#, elp.AoN_SII_#, elp.V_SII_#, elp.V_SII_#, elp.V_OI_#, elp.bpt, elp.V_HeII_# FROM MyDB.Nuc_dwarfs as nd CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (nd.ra, nd.dec, #) as w JOIN SpecObjAll so ON so.specObjID = w.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort as elp ON so.specObjid = elp.specObjid
